# Astro build-time public vars.
#
# You normally do NOT need to set this. The feedback page already defaults to the
# real production Turnstile site key, so the Cloudflare Workers Builds production
# build embeds the right widget with no extra config. `just wrangler-dev` builds
# with the Turnstile *test* key so the widget passes on localhost.
#
# Set this only to OVERRIDE the built-in default (e.g. after rotating the widget)
# for a local production build/preview. This value is a PUBLIC site key (rendered
# into the page HTML) — not a secret. Its secret counterpart is the
# TURNSTILE_SECRET Worker secret (wrangler secret put).
PUBLIC_TURNSTILE_SITE_KEY=0x4AAAAAAD7jYecPL3c82-lW
